ce/pane {\"id\":3,\"icon\":\"fe_check\",\"uniqueID\":\"_82e042-48\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-pane kt-accordion-pane kt-accordion-pane-3 kt-pane_82e042-48\"><div class=\"kt-accordion-header-wrap\"><button class=\"kt-blocks-accordion-header kt-acccordion-button-label-show\"><span class=\"kt-blocks-accordion-title-wrap\"><span class=\"kt-blocks-accordion-title\">What games can I play here?</span><div style=\"display:inline-flex;justify-content:center;align-items:center\" class=\"kt-btn-svg-icon kt-btn-svg-icon-fe_check kt-btn-side-right\"><svg style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" height=\"24\" width=\"24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"></polyline></svg></div></span><span class=\"kt-blocks-accordion-icon-trigger\"></span></button></div><div class=\"kt-accordion-panel\"><div class=\"kt-accordion-panel-inner\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>With thousands of games in our library, it would be easier to say what games you can\'t play online with us. In short, we have lots of slot machines, a fair number of table games including online blackjack and roulette, and games run by live dealers.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:kadence/pane -->\n\n<!-- wp:kadence/pane {\"id\":4,\"icon\":\"fe_check\",\"uniqueID\":\"_7dfa23-3e\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-pane kt-accordion-pane kt-accordion-pane-4 kt-pane_7dfa23-3e\"><div class=\"kt-accordion-header-wrap\"><button class=\"kt-blocks-accordion-header kt-acccordion-button-label-show\"><span class=\"kt-blocks-accordion-title-wrap\"><span class=\"kt-blocks-accordion-title\">Are there bonuses at Mason Slots?</span><div style=\"display:inline-flex;justify-content:center;align-items:center\" class=\"kt-btn-svg-icon kt-btn-svg-icon-fe_check kt-btn-side-right\"><svg style=\"display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" height=\"24\" width=\"24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"20 6 9 17 4 12\"></polyline></svg></div></span><span class=\"kt-blocks-accordion-icon-trigger\"></span></button></div><div class=\"kt-accordion-panel\"><div class=\"kt-accordion-panel-inner\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Of course! Being a part of the lodge means receiving regular bonuses. First and foremost, there is a welcome bonus for newcomers. Then, there are weekly reload deals. Finally, we have tournaments and the Wheel of Fortune for the ultimate fun.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:kadence/pane --></div></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:kadence/accordion -->\n\n<!-- wp:template-part {\"slug\":\"footer\",\"theme\":\"twentytwentytwo\",\"tagName\":\"footer\"} /-->', 'Главная страница', 'Отображение в качестве главной страницы сайта или страницы записей, если статическая главная страница не задана.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '32-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-04-20 20:40:49', '2022-04-20 17:40:49', '', 32, 'http://test/?p=171', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
